description.en-US:
The Smart Business Hall product focuses on service improvement.

 On the one hand, it strictly supervises the implementation of service norms and standards to ensure that every customer can receive high-quality services;
 On the other hand, it continuously collects operational data, and provides a solid basis for process optimization through multi-dimensional analysis of information such as business processing time and customer flow;
 At the same time, it directly measures the service status obtained by users through intelligent means, accurately insights into customer experience, timely discovers and solves pain points and deficiencies in services, and helps the service level of business halls to continuously improve.

Application Scenarios: E-commerce, manufacturing, retail, etc.

Implemented Functions:
 Provide data integration services for mainstream ERP vendors such as UFIDA, Kingdee, and Digiwin Software. Through research on specific scenarios, select encapsulated call integration mode or intermediate object integration mode to integrate data between systems, and realize various functions such as warehouse modeling, warehousing management, outbound management, in-warehouse management, and warehouse visualization.

Application Value:
 Improve management efficiency and reduce human errors and costs;
 Optimize inventory control: Real-time update of inventory information, realize dynamic adjustment and optimization of inventory, reduce inventory backlog and waste;
 Improve customer satisfaction: Shorten order processing and delivery time, improve customer satisfaction, and provide real-time inventory information and order status inquiry services;
 Enhance enterprise competitiveness: Improve management efficiency and accuracy, reduce operating costs, and enhance enterprise market competitiveness;
 Data-supported decision-making: Provide enterprises with comprehensive real-time data and reports to support enterprises in formulating and implementing more precise strategies;
 In summary, ensure unimpeded data flow within the enterprise, avoid the formation of information silos, and thus maximize the value and role of information systems, information modules, and enterprise data.

Application Location: Logistics Industry

Application Difficulties:
 Smudges, occlusions, and wrinkles on express waybills affect recognition accuracy;
 Requires high concurrency and fast sorting, and realizes automatic sorting in cooperation with cross-belt conveyors.

Key Technologies:
 Automatically identify the "barcode" and "three-segment code" information on the logistics waybill of express parcels running at high speed on the conveyor belt. The "barcode" is uniquely associated with the express parcel, and the "three-segment code" provides the sorting destination, comprehensively realizing automatic sorting of express parcels;
 When the express parcel moves on the conveyor belt, it triggers the photoelectric sensor to control the industrial camera to take photos;
 The captured images are preprocessed and then identified by algorithms. The core algorithm models include:
 Waybill Positioning: Identify the "waybill" area in the image through positioning algorithms;
 Text Detection: Detect the text part in the "waybill" area through detection algorithms to obtain the text parts of "three-segment code" and "barcode";
 Text Recognition: Recognize the text content of "three-segment code" and "barcode" through recognition algorithms, and output the results after identifying the character content.

Application Value:
 Save labor costs;
 High efficiency and accuracy, completely solve misjudgments caused by human eye fatigue;
 Reduce customer complaint rate;
 Stable work for a long time;
 Reduce material loss;
 Recognition rate is as high as 97%;
 Can detect numbers in various code systems of STO, YTO, ZTO, SF and Yunda.

The airport security platform adheres to the design concept of "Massive, Intelligent Integration, Scenario-Based", and builds "One Platform, One Map, One Sky Network".

**"One Platform"** realizes access to various security equipment and integrated docking of multiple systems to ensure interconnection and interoperability of business systems;

**"One Map"** integrates security elements with the help of GIS maps to realize visual management;

**"One Sky Network"** makes security situation visible and decision-making data-driven through AI and digital technologies, comprehensively improving the comprehensive management and unified scheduling capabilities of airport security.

Core Function List:
 Standard dress detection for staff in the operation room (chef uniforms, chef hats, masks);
 Rodent infestation detection in the operation room;
 Trash can cover detection;
 Fire detection (warehouse);
 People counting;
 Social distance monitoring;
 Fire exit congestion identification;
 Left item detection;
 Mobile alarm system (real-time alarm push via WeChat official account);
 Monitoring large screen.

Defect detection is a key link in industrial manufacturing and production, and also the main application scenario of industrial vision technology.

 There are currently multiple detection methods: Manual visual inspection relies on a large number of workers, is greatly affected by the working environment, requires long-term training, and is difficult to digitize due to reliance on experience, resulting in unstable quality, inconsistent standards, and lack of data statistics and traceability; Traditional machine vision detection can detect and measure defects with clear features, based on rules and programming, with high deployment efficiency and can partially replace manual labor, but cannot continuously learn and iterate, only realizing partial digitization;

AI + computer vision detection has stronger detection capabilities, can detect random and irregular flaws, and can completely replace manual labor. Although the R&D cycle is long and deployment cost is high, the detection model can continuously learn and iterate to realize complete digital business management.
